\begin_layout Standard
已知
\begin_inset Formula $a>1$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $b>1$
\end_inset

, 求证
\begin_inset Formula $\log_{a}ab+\log_{b}ab\ge4$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
这题比较简单, 首先想到恒等式
\begin_inset Formula $\log_{x}y=\frac{\log y}{\log x}$
\end_inset

对于所有正实数
\begin_inset Formula $x,y$
\end_inset

都成立, 所以
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
LHS=\frac{\log ab}{\log a}+\frac{\log ab}{\log b}=\log ab\paren{\frac{1}{\log a}+\frac{1}{\log b}}
\]

\end_inset

另外恒等式
\begin_inset Formula $\log ab=\log a+\log b$
\end_inset

对于所有的正实数
\begin_inset Formula $a,b$
\end_inset

都成立.
 另外, 因为
\begin_inset Formula $x>1$
\end_inset

时
\begin_inset Formula $\log x>0$
\end_inset

.
 所以如果用均值不等式, 则有
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\log ab}{\log a}+\frac{\log ab}{\log b}=1+\frac{\log b}{\log a}+\frac{\log a}{\log b}+1\ge1+2\sqrt{\frac{\log b}{\log a}\cdot\frac{\log a}{\log b}}+1=4
\]

\end_inset

如果考虑使用Cauchy不等式, 则有
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\log ab\paren{\frac{1}{\log a}+\frac{1}{\log b}}=\paren{\log a+\log b}\paren{\frac{1}{\log a}+\frac{1}{\log b}}\ge\paren{1+1}^{2}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
2.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $x_{1}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{2}$
\end_inset

是方程
\begin_inset Formula $x^{2}-x+1=0$
\end_inset

的两个根, 求
\begin_inset Formula $x_{1}^{1980}+\paren{\frac{1}{x_{2}}}^{1980}$
\end_inset

的值.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
次数真高, 但是因为有个倒数, 而且韦达定理说两根的积
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x_{1}x_{2}=1
\]

\end_inset

这样可以求出来
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{1}{x_{2}}=x_{1}$
\end_inset

, 但代入最后的式子里还是次数太高, 变成了
\begin_inset Formula $2x_{1}^{1980}$
\end_inset

.
 但是这一不是不可求解的, 因为
\begin_inset Formula $x_{1}$
\end_inset

是方程
\begin_inset Formula $x^{2}-x+1=0$
\end_inset

的根, 所以
\begin_inset Formula $x_{1}^{2}=x_{1}-1$
\end_inset

, 这样两边乘以
\begin_inset Formula $x_{1}^{n}$
\end_inset

, 并记
\begin_inset Formula $X_{n}=x_{1}^{n}$
\end_inset

就会出现
\begin_inset Formula $X_{n+2}=X_{n+1}-X_{n}$
\end_inset

这刚好是一个递推公式, 而且可以计算出
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
X_{0}=1,X_{1}=2x_{1},X_{2}=2x_{1}-1,X_{3}=-1,X_{4}=-2x_{1},X_{5}=-2x_{1}+1,X_{6}=1,X_{7}=2x_{1}
\]

\end_inset

这样一直算下来形成了一个周期, 也是太巧了, 可以看出
\begin_inset Formula $X_{k+6}=X_{k}$
\end_inset

, 但是证明的话还是要用归纳法或者自然数的良序性.
 所以只需要知道
\begin_inset Formula $1980=6\times330$
\end_inset

便知
\begin_inset Formula $X_{1980}=X_{0}=1$
\end_inset

, 注意
\begin_inset Formula $X_{n}=x_{1}^{n}$
\end_inset

而要求的结果是
\begin_inset Formula $2x_{1}^{1980}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

